    <entry>
      <title>PHP语句结束符</title>
      <link href="/blog/PHP%E8%AF%AD%E5%8F%A5%E7%BB%93%E6%9D%9F%E7%AC%A6/"/>
      <url>/blog/PHP%E8%AF%AD%E5%8F%A5%E7%BB%93%E6%9D%9F%E7%AC%A6/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<link rel="stylesheet" class="aplayer-secondary-style-marker" href="\assets\css\APlayer.min.css"><script src="\assets\js\APlayer.min.js" class="aplayer-secondary-script-marker"></script><h1 id="PHP语句分隔符"><a href="#PHP语句分隔符" class="headerlink" title="PHP语句分隔符"></a>PHP语句分隔符</h1><blockquote><p>语句分隔符：在PHP中，代码是以行为单位，系统需要通过判断行的结束，该结束通常都是一个分号“ ; ”。（英文状态下）</p></blockquote><h2 id="定义内容："><a href="#定义内容：" class="headerlink" title="定义内容："></a>定义内容：</h2><figure class="highlight php"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">&lt;?php</span> </span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//例子1：</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="variable">$a</span> = <span class="number">5</span>;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//例子2：</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">echo</span> <span class="string">&#x27;hello&#x27;</span>;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">?&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight php"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">&lt;?php</span> </span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">//语句结束符的使用</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">echo</span> <span class="string">&#x27;hello world&#x27;</span>;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">?&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><font color = 'orange'>错误示例：</font><br>    <img src="2.jpg" alt=""></p><p><font color = 'orange'>特殊说明：</font></p><ol><li>PHP中标记结束符“ ?&gt; ”有自带语句结束符的效果，最后一行PHP代码可以没有语句结束符“ ; ”。</li><li>PHP中其实有很多代码的书写并不是嵌入到HTML中，而是单独存在，通常书写习惯中就不建议使用标记结束符，PHP会自动从开始到最后全部认为是PHP代码，从而解析。</li></ol>]]></content>
      
      
